---
description: Use before finalizing code, config, spec, doc, or CI changes to choose and report minimal verification checks.
alwaysApply: false
---

Before marking work complete:
- Run the smallest relevant verification set (tests, lint, typecheck, build, or project-specific checks).
- If checks fail, fix issues or report blocker with failing command and key error.
- Do not claim completion without verification unless user explicitly skips it.
- In final summary, report checks run, pass/fail status, and skipped checks with reason.
